Close, but no cigar, in my opinion. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uardonicsongcaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ardonic Songcaster</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 11:16:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22895.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.gwi.net/~tadpole/everquest/thegrove/images/aniunder.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Not quite done right, I think...</span><hr size=1> E=MC2 <p>-Ardonic Songcaster <BR>
